Question Chapter 4

Choose 1 of product in group project (if kerepek, select kerepek bawang product)

a) Generate coding for case study (kerepek bawang ) with fulfill JQUERY core concept (syntax, DOM manipulation, css styling, event handling).

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Kerepek Bawang</title>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        .highlight {
            background-color: yellow;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1 id="title">Kerepek Bawang</h1>
    <button id="changeColor">Change Title Color</button>
    <ul id="kerepekList">
        <li>Kerepek Bawang Pedas</li>
        <li>Kerepek Bawang Cheese</li>
        <li>Kerepek Bawang Original</li>
    </ul>
    <button id="highlightItems">Highlight Items</button>

    <script>
        // Event handling and CSS styling
        $("#changeColor").click(function () {
            $("#title").css("color", "blue");
        });

        // DOM manipulation
        $("#highlightItems").click(function () {
            $("#kerepekList li").addClass("highlight");
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>


b) Generate coding for case study (kerepek bawang ) with fulfill JSON DATA TYPES (DATA TYPES:string, numbers, booleans, null, arrays, objects).

const kerepekBawang = {
    name: "Kerepek Bawang",
    price: 12.5,
    inStock: true,
    flavors: ["Pedas", "Cheese", "Original"],
    details: null
};

console.log(kerepekBawang.name); // String
console.log(kerepekBawang.price); // Number
console.log(kerepekBawang.inStock); // Boolean
console.log(kerepekBawang.details); // Null
console.log(kerepekBawang.flavors); // Array

c) Generate coding for case study (kerepek bawang ) with fulfill JSON DATASTRUCTURE (arrays, objects, nested structures)

const kerepekProducts = {
    category: "Snacks",
    products: [
        {
            name: "Kerepek Bawang Pedas",
            price: 12.5,
            inStock: true
        },
        {
            name: "Kerepek Bawang Cheese",
            price: 14.0,
            inStock: false
        }
    ]
};

// Accessing nested structures
console.log(kerepekProducts.products[0].name); // Output: Kerepek Bawang Pedas
console.log(kerepekProducts.products[1].inStock); // Output: false


d) Generate coding for case study (kerepek bawang ) with fulfill JSON pasring, stringification

const kerepekJSON = '{"name": "Kerepek Bawang", "price": 12.5, "inStock": true}';

// Parsing JSON
const kerepekObject = JSON.parse(kerepekJSON);
console.log(kerepekObject.name); // Output: Kerepek Bawang

// Stringifying Object
const newKerepek = {
    name: "Kerepek Bawang Cheese",
    price: 14.0,
    inStock: false
};
const newKerepekJSON = JSON.stringify(newKerepek);
console.log(newKerepekJSON);
// Output: {"name":"Kerepek Bawang Cheese","price":14,"inStock":false}
